        "creation_date": 1581601561,
        "body": "<blockquote>\n<p>ACTION_TAG_DISCOVERED:<\/p>\n<p>This intent is started if no activities handle the ACTION_NDEF_DISCOVERED or ACTION_TECH_DISCOVERED intents.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/connectivity/nfc/nfc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/connectivity/nfc/nfc<\/a><\/p>\n<p>You get this Intent when no others has captured it, so there is something wrong in your setup.<\/p>\n<p>You can capture it explicitly like:<\/p>\n<pre><code>&lt;intent-filter&gt;\n    &lt;action android:name=&quot;android.nfc.action.TAG_DISCOVERED&quot;/&gt;\n&lt;/intent-filter&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
        "answer_id": 60209332,
        "question_id": 60208659,
        "last_edit_date": 1592644375
    }],
